{"tid":158481,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去過沖繩外島","createTime":"2017-03-16T09:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T03:48:38.000Z","uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6629343cb5e2e36c623117499ea8e9722630d2f9","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T09:57:42.000Z","msg":"黎近打算去 渡嘉敷島,座間味島,阿嘉島,  3日2夜<br />\n<br />\n睇左交通, <br />\n第1日 阿嘉, 之後答船去座間味<br />\n第2日 座間味, 之後答船去渡嘉敷<br />\n第3日 渡嘉敷, 玩完番沖繩<br />\n<br />\n渡嘉敷 / 座間味 有無住宿推薦?<br />\n<br />\n另外  阿波連&gt;渡嘉志久沙灘&gt;碼頭  有無巴士??"},{"pid":"1a52c0a68bf85b9ba73740d1436a90fab726850b","tid":158481,"uid":59998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"上年去過沖繩，未去外島，今年想去外島。可以一齊研究下啊"},{"pid":"5c5f545d96cde3fc7f385a531735fa08c6d9462f","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年去過沖繩，未去外島，今年想去外島。可以一齊研究下啊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n座間味村<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vill.zamami.okinawa.jp.t.gz.hp.transer.com/map/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vill.zamami.okinawa.jp.t.gz.hp.transer.com%2Fmap%2F&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=08e4d64d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vill.zamami.okinawa.jp.t.gz.hp.transer.com/map/</a> \t<br />\n<br />\n渡嘉敷島<br />\n巴士時間表 <a href=\"http://www.vill.tokashiki.okinawa.jp/pdf/basu.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vill.tokashiki.okinawa.jp%2Fpdf%2Fbasu.pdf&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=07982198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vill.tokashiki.okinawa.jp/pdf/basu.pdf</a>   <br />\n<br />\n睇唔明日文, 係咪即係話要去 渡嘉志久ビーチ 的話, 就要上車後講明? 咁走個陣點算?"},{"pid":"b3339be49120105b436ef96941cf1865a3a7444b","tid":158481,"uid":59998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"去座間味島要一早訂船票，否則去到先買未必有位。"},{"pid":"e0c96c74b2637071276f69cb4ba896ce7434f039","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去座間味島要一早訂船票，否則去到先買未必有位。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前1日先到沖繩...唔知得唔得呢?"},{"pid":"ae1c3233ca695a30bcac7a0ee026e7f83921c05f","tid":158481,"uid":36037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去座間味島要一早訂船票，否則去到先買未必有位。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前1日先到沖繩...唔知得唔得呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過閒日去，大把位，你呢啲天氣應該仲少人，座間味島上面有兩個沙灘，去遠啲 東面果個靚好多"},{"pid":"0a78c332756aa353089edb625a264f038104b551","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T17:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去座間味島要一早訂船票，否則去到先買未必有位。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我前1日先到沖繩...唔知得唔得呢?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過閒日去，大把位，你呢啲天氣應該仲少人，座間味島上面有兩個沙灘，去遠啲 東面果個靚好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我６月中既星期五呀<br />\n<br />\n師兄有無去過渡嘉敷島？<br />\n<br />\n諗緊去唔去埋渡嘉志久沙灘。。但Ｄ人又話水底唔多靚，係有機會見到海龜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有無玩埋潛水？<br />\n<br />\n已準備好潛水鏡＋ＦＩＮ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffcfc941de1350f16a2e69dfe1bd15cab8cac75","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98f4340914e0e2c4960cd6754c403283ecb928b5","tid":158481,"uid":87714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:48:38.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}